casebody.data:
O’CONNOR v. DIRECTOR OF PATUXENT INSTITUTION [App. No. 71,

September Term, 1964.]

Decided February 12, 1965.

Before Prescott, C. J., and Hammond, Marbury, Sybert and Barnes, JJ.

Per Curiam.

For the reasons assigned by Judge Parker in his opinion below, the application will be denied.

Application denied.
